text: Josef Škvor (born 8 December 1929) is a Czech gymnast. He competed at the 1952 Summer Olympics and the 1956 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1929 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Czech male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Czechoslovakia Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1956 Summer Olympics
